---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Ultrasonic Scaling" 
  category="Advanced Cleaning"
  description="With ultrasonic scaling, we glide a vibrating scale tip over the surface of your teeth for a fast and smooth finish, making cleanings more comfortable and efficient."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606811841689-23dfddce3e95?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Advanced Cleaning Technology</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        With ultrasonic scaling, we glide a vibrating scale tip over the surface of your teeth 
        for a fast and smooth finish. This advanced technology makes dental cleanings more comfortable, 
        efficient, and thorough than traditional manual scaling alone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      What is Ultrasonic Scaling?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Ultrasonic scaling uses high-frequency sound waves to break up plaque and tartar deposits 
            on your teeth. The ultrasonic scaler tip vibrates at approximately 25,000-50,000 times per 
            second, creating tiny bubbles in the water that implode and help dislodge bacteria and debris.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">How It Works</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
              <span><strong>Ultrasonic vibrations</strong> break apart tartar and plaque</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">2</span>
              </div>
              <span><strong>Water irrigation</strong> flushes away loosened debris</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
              <span><strong>Cavitation bubbles</strong> disrupt bacterial biofilms</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">4</span>
              </div>
              <span><strong>Gentle tip motion</strong> requires minimal pressure</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="w-72 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-200/30 rounded-lg shadow-md flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Ultrasonic vs. Traditional Hand Scaling
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Traditional Hand Scaling -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
          </svg>
          <span>Traditional Hand Scaling</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-orange-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Method:</strong> Manual scraping with metal instruments</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-orange-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Pressure:</strong> Requires more force to remove tartar</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-orange-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Time:</strong> More time-consuming process</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-orange-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Comfort:</strong> Can be more uncomfortable</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-orange-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Precision:</strong> Excellent for detailed work</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-orange-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Noise:</strong> Quiet procedure</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ultrasonic Scaling -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100/30 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-blue-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
          <span>Ultrasonic Scaling</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Method:</strong> High-frequency vibrations + water</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Pressure:</strong> Gentle touch, less force needed</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Time:</strong> Faster removal of large deposits</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Comfort:</strong> More comfortable experience</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Precision:</strong> Excellent for bulk tartar removal</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong>Noise:</strong> Some vibration sound present</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Advantages of Ultrasonic Scaling
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Enhanced Comfort -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3 text-center">Enhanced Comfort</h3>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
          <li>• Requires less pressure on teeth and gums</li>
          <li>• Reduces scraping sensation</li>
          <li>• Cooling water spray provides comfort</li>
          <li>• Less post-treatment sensitivity</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Improved Efficiency -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-3 text-center">Improved Efficiency</h3>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
          <li>• Faster removal of heavy tartar deposits</li>
          <li>• Shorter overall appointment times</li>
          <li>• More thorough cleaning in difficult areas</li>
          <li>• Reduces hand fatigue for hygienists</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Better Results -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-3 text-center">Superior Cleaning</h3>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
          <li>• Disrupts bacterial biofilms effectively</li>
          <li>• Reaches into deep pockets better</li>
          <li>• Flushes bacteria with water irrigation</li>
          <li>• Smoother tooth surface finish</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Ultrasonic Scaling Process
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-blue-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Assessment & Preparation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              We examine your teeth and gums to determine the extent of tartar buildup and identify 
              any sensitive areas. The ultrasonic unit is prepared with the appropriate power setting 
              and water flow for your needs.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Customization:</strong> Power and frequency adjusted based on tartar hardness and sensitivity
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Ultrasonic Cleaning</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              The ultrasonic scaler tip is gently guided along your teeth, using vibrations to break up tartar. 
              A continuous water spray cools the area and washes away debris. The process feels like a gentle 
              tickling or vibrating sensation.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Technique:</strong> Light, overlapping strokes with minimal pressure for maximum effectiveness
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-blue-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Hand Scaling Refinement</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              After ultrasonic scaling removes the bulk deposits, we may use traditional hand instruments 
              for detailed work in specific areas that need extra attention or precision cleaning.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Best of both:</strong> Combines efficiency of ultrasonics with precision of hand scaling
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Polish & Fluoride</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Your teeth are polished to remove surface stains and create a smooth finish. 
              A fluoride treatment may be applied to strengthen enamel and reduce sensitivity.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Final result:</strong> Clean, smooth teeth that feel fresh and look brighter
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Who Benefits Most from Ultrasonic Scaling?
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Ideal Candidates</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Heavy tartar buildup:</strong> Especially effective for thick, stubborn deposits</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Sensitive patients:</strong> More comfortable than aggressive hand scaling</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Periodontal patients:</strong> Better access to deep pockets</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Time-conscious patients:</strong> Faster appointments</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Implant patients:</strong> Safer around implants with proper tips</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Special Considerations</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-300 p-4">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-2">Pacemaker Patients</h4>
              <p class="text-yellow-700 text-sm">
                Modern pacemakers are generally safe with ultrasonics, but we'll verify 
                with your cardiologist if you have an older device.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-300 p-4">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Hearing Sensitivity</h4>
              <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">
                Some patients find the ultrasonic sound uncomfortable. We can adjust 
                settings or use ear protection if needed.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-300 p-4">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">Dental Work</h4>
              <p class="text-green-700 text-sm">
                Safe for most dental work. Special tips are available for implants, 
                and we avoid certain restorations when necessary.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      After Your Ultrasonic Scaling
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">What to Expect</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Teeth may feel extra smooth and clean</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Minimal bleeding, less than traditional scaling</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Less post-treatment sensitivity</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Can return to normal activities immediately</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Home Care Tips</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Resume normal brushing and flossing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Use antimicrobial mouthwash if recommended</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Stay hydrated to help flush bacteria</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Schedule follow-up appointments as recommended</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Experience Advanced Dental Cleaning
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Discover the comfort and efficiency of ultrasonic scaling technology. Our advanced cleaning 
        methods provide superior results with enhanced comfort, making your dental visits more pleasant 
        and effective.
